WEBVTT

NOTE: Estimated from known TTS script; timing requires human review before Tier 1 captions.

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:09.659
If you need to sell your house fast in Northampton, Massachusetts, USA Home Buyers gives you a simpler option than listing, repairing, and waiting.

2
00:00:09.659 --> 00:00:14.489
We buy houses as-is for cash in Northampton and throughout Hampshire County.

3
00:00:14.489 --> 00:00:17.709
This is built for homeowners who want certainty.

4
00:00:17.709 --> 00:00:28.173
The house might need repairs, have old systems, be part of an estate, have tenants, or simply be a property you no longer want to manage.

5
00:00:28.173 --> 00:00:35.418
You do not have to paint, clean out every room, schedule open houses, or keep renegotiating after inspections.

6
00:00:35.418 --> 00:00:37.918
Our process is direct.

7
00:00:37.918 --> 00:00:43.955
Tell us about the property, share the basics, and we will review it with you.

8
00:00:43.955 --> 00:00:46.772
Then we make a written cash offer.

9
00:00:46.772 --> 00:00:51.200
If it fits what you need, you pick the closing date.

10
00:00:51.200 --> 00:00:57.237
If it does not fit, you can walk away with no pressure and no fee.

11
00:00:57.237 --> 00:01:01.261
We are not agents, and we do not charge commissions.

12
00:01:01.261 --> 00:01:11.323
We buy Northampton-area homes in their current condition and focus on making the sale predictable, including the closing timeline and next steps for your family.

13
00:01:11.323 --> 00:01:15.750
For a no-obligation cash offer, call USA Home Buyers at 888-274-5006.

14
00:01:15.750 --> 00:01:21.300
We will listen first, explain the process clearly, and help you decide the best next move.
